  "text": "### 4.2 Interest Calculation  \n- **Accrual:** Calculated daily, paid monthly\n- **Payment Date:** Last business day of each month\n- **Tiering:** Tiered rates apply to balance as of payment date  \n**Example (30-day month):**\n- Opening balance: £10,000 (Tier 1: 4.50%)\n- Interest accrual: £10,000 × 4.50% ÷ 365 days × 30 days = £36.99\n- Paid on: Last business day of month",
